## ğŸ¤ Contributing

Contributions are welcome! Here's how:

1. **ğŸ› Report Bugs**: [Open an issue](https://github.com/navam-io/navam-invest/issues)
2. **ğŸ’¡ Suggest Features**: [Start a discussion](https://github.com/navam-io/navam-invest/discussions)
3. **ğŸ“ Improve Docs**: Submit PR for documentation
4. **ğŸ”§ Submit Code**: Fork, branch, PR

### Development Workflow

```bash
# 1. Create feature branch
git checkout -b feature/your-feature

# 2. Make changes and test
pytest && black src/ tests/

# 3. Commit and push
git commit -m "feat: add your feature"
git push origin feature/your-feature

# 4. Open Pull Request
```

See `CLAUDE.md` for comprehensive agent development guide.

